  "summaries": [
    {
      "id": 25809,
      "category": "team",
      "content": "## Summary\nAn issue discovered in Yoti's marketing website (www.yoti.com) WordPress implementation. The vulnerability exposes admin usernames through WordPress API endpoints.\n\n## Steps to Reproduce\n1. Search Shodan using query `org:yoti.com`\n2. Access the identified IP: `http://185.116.54.11`\n3. Add the following parameters to access WordPress API endpoints:\n   - `/wp-json`\n   - `/wp-json/wp/v2/users`\n\n\n## Impact\nThe vulnerability exposes admin usernames through WordPress API endpoints",
